text: Everything this stall sells is good because of Guy Chef(Clean & Super friendly)but it's always the China Lady who spoils the show with Bad China unfriendly Attitude!! Never change always Bad Service don't ever go if u see China Lady serving ! Spoils ur mood !
Seems like the rice is left over from day before. One could taste the difference if the rice is freshly cooked.

Pricey. The funniest part is they have bbq fish and fried fish. And the bbq fish is already fried, and they just leave the fried fish on the bbq stove for a while and then call it bbq fish haha. All in addition to the burnt meat and bad attitude staff.
Attitude women. Like i owe her money.
